  "texts": [
    "Eventually, a topic was assigned to each tweet.",
    "We labeled each topic based on the most frequent term in the corresponding topic representation.",
    "To explore the most frequent topics for each month, we grouped tweets based on their post dates and ranked the topic frequency within each month.",
    "To probe deeper into our analysis, we chose a set of potentially controversial topics, aiming to explore both the sentiment towards each topic and its change over time.",
    "Building upon the sentiment analysis conducted in Section 3.3, we delved deeper into these chosen topics."
